		<label>Chaos Insurgency</label>
		<description>A terrorist group of former SCP Foundation personnel who have defected and stolen several SCPs from them. They use anomalies to build a utopian future for their members alone, where they are the master of everything. They employ SCP's whenever advantageous and steal others to achieve their goals. They often test on lone, unsuspecting, innocent colonies and tribes much like the SCP-Foundation does on convicted D-Class prisoners. While they do maintain a visible base or two, they largely operate in roaming groups. The Chaos Insurgency notably made a pact with a large number of SCP-1788-1 instances, promising them an unlimited amount of satiation for their blood lust in exchange for being the "muscle" that captures victims for experimentation.</description>
